question: Bring out the only incorrect statement:
option1: Allahabad High Court has Maximum number of sanctioned Judges in India
option2: Uttar Pradesh shares its border with 8 states
option3: Sultan Sikandar Lodi was the first to move his capital from Delhi to Agra
option4: Aligarh Muslim University was originally established by an act of parliament
answer: Aligarh Muslim University was originally established by an act of parliament
explanation: Aligarh Muslim University was originally founded by Sir Syed Ahmed Khan in 1875 as Muhammadan Anglo Oriental College
